lead_paragraph: Mike Trout went 3 for 3 and made an impressive first-inning catch, leading the Los Angeles Angels to an 8-2 victory over the Oakland Athletics on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Trout Gets 3 Hits in LA Angels' 8-2 Victory Over Oakland A's
